{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"This room may appear"},{"time":2000,"text":"to be holding 600 people,"},{"time":4000,"text":"but there's actually so many more,"},{"time":6000,"text":"because in each one of us"},{"time":8000,"text":"there is a multitude of personalities."},{"time":11000,"text":"I have two primary personalities"},{"time":14000,"text":"that have been in conflict and conversation within me"},{"time":16000,"text":"since I was a little girl."},{"time":18000,"text":"I call them \"the mystic\""},{"time":20000,"text":"and \"the warrior.\""},{"time":22000,"text":"I was born into a family"},{"time":24000,"text":"of politically active,"},{"time":26000,"text":"intellectual atheists."},{"time":28000,"text":"There was this equation in my family that went something like this:"},{"time":31000,"text":"if you are intelligent,"},{"time":33000,"text":"you therefore are not spiritual."},{"time":36000,"text":"I was the freak of the family."},{"time":38000,"text":"I was this weird little kid"},{"time":40000,"text":"who wanted to have deep talks"},{"time":42000,"text":"about the worlds that might exist"},{"time":45000,"text":"beyond the ones that we perceive with our senses."},{"time":48000,"text":"I wanted to know"},{"time":50000,"text":"if what we human beings see"},{"time":52000,"text":"and hear and think"},{"time":55000,"text":"is a full and accurate picture"},{"time":57000,"text":"of reality."},{"time":59000,"text":"So, looking for answers,"},{"time":61000,"text":"I went to Catholic mass."},{"time":63000,"text":"I tagged along with my neighbors."},{"time":65000,"text":"I read Sartre and Socrates."},{"time":67000,"text":"And then a wonderful thing happened"},{"time":69000,"text":"when I was in high school:"},{"time":71000,"text":"Gurus from the East"},{"time":73000,"text":"started washing up on the shores of America."},{"time":76000,"text":"And I said to myself,"},{"time":78000,"text":"\"I wanna get me one of them.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"And ever since,"},{"time":82000,"text":"I've been walking the mystic path,"},{"time":85000,"text":"trying to peer beyond"},{"time":87000,"text":"what Albert Einstein called"},{"time":89000,"text":"\"the optical delusion"},{"time":91000,"text":"of everyday consciousness.\""},{"time":94000,"text":"So what did he mean by this? I'll show you."},{"time":97000,"text":"Take a breath right now"},{"time":99000,"text":"of this clear air in this room."},{"time":103000,"text":"Now, see this strange,"},{"time":106000,"text":"underwater,"},{"time":109000,"text":"coral reef-looking thing?"},{"time":111000,"text":"It's actually a person's trachea,"},{"time":114000,"text":"and those colored globs"},{"time":116000,"text":"are microbes"},{"time":118000,"text":"that are actually swimming around in this room"},{"time":120000,"text":"right now, all around us."},{"time":123000,"text":"If we're blind to this simple biology,"},{"time":126000,"text":"imagine what we're missing"},{"time":129000,"text":"at the smallest subatomic level right now"},{"time":132000,"text":"and at the grandest cosmic levels."},{"time":135000,"text":"My years as a mystic"},{"time":138000,"text":"have made me question"},{"time":140000,"text":"almost all my assumptions."},{"time":142000,"text":"They've made me a proud I-don't-know-it-all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"Now when the mystic part of me"},{"time":148000,"text":"jabbers on and on like this,"},{"time":150000,"text":"the warrior rolls her eyes."},{"time":153000,"text":"She's concerned"},{"time":156000,"text":"about what's happening in this world right now."},{"time":160000,"text":"She's worried."},{"time":162000,"text":"She says, \"Excuse me, I'm pissed off,"},{"time":165000,"text":"and I know a few things,"},{"time":167000,"text":"and we better get busy about them right now.\""},{"time":169000,"text":"I've spent my life as a warrior,"},{"time":171000,"text":"working for women's issues,"},{"time":173000,"text":"working on political campaigns,"},{"time":176000,"text":"being an activist for the environment."},{"time":179000,"text":"And it can be sort of crazy-making,"},{"time":182000,"text":"housing both the mystic and the warrior"},{"time":184000,"text":"in one body."},{"time":186000,"text":"I've always been attracted"},{"time":189000,"text":"to those rare people"},{"time":191000,"text":"who pull that off,"},{"time":193000,"text":"who devote their lives to humanity"},{"time":195000,"text":"with the grit of the warrior"},{"time":197000,"text":"and the grace of the mystic --"},{"time":200000,"text":"people like Martin Luther King, Jr.,"},{"time":203000,"text":"who wrote, \"I can never be"},{"time":205000,"text":"what I ought to be"},{"time":207000,"text":"until you are"},{"time":209000,"text":"what you ought to be."},{"time":211000,"text":"This,\" he wrote, \"is the interrelated structure"},{"time":214000,"text":"of reality.\""},{"time":216000,"text":"Then Mother Teresa, another mystic warrior,"},{"time":219000,"text":"who said, \"The problem with the world"},{"time":222000,"text":"is that we draw the circle of our family"},{"time":225000,"text":"too small.\""},{"time":227000,"text":"And Nelson Mandela,"},{"time":229000,"text":"who lives by the African concept"},{"time":231000,"text":"of \"ubuntu,\""},{"time":233000,"text":"which means \"I need you"},{"time":235000,"text":"in order to be me,"},{"time":237000,"text":"and you need me in order to be you.\""},{"time":240000,"text":"Now we all love to trot out"},{"time":242000,"text":"these three mystic warriors"},{"time":244000,"text":"as if they were born"},{"time":246000,"text":"with the saint gene."},{"time":248000,"text":"But we all actually have"},{"time":250000,"text":"the same capacity that they do,"},{"time":253000,"text":"and we need to do"},{"time":255000,"text":"their work now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":257000,"text":"I'm deeply disturbed"},{"time":259000,"text":"by the ways in which all of our cultures"},{"time":262000,"text":"are demonizing \"the Other\""},{"time":265000,"text":"by the voice we're giving"},{"time":267000,"text":"to the most divisive among us."},{"time":270000,"text":"Listen to these titles"},{"time":272000,"text":"of some of the bestselling books"},{"time":274000,"text":"from both sides of the political divide"},{"time":276000,"text":"here in the U.S."},{"time":278000,"text":"\"Liberalism Is a Mental Disorder,\""},{"time":281000,"text":"\"Rush Limbaugh Is a Big Fat Idiot,\""},{"time":284000,"text":"\"Pinheads and Patriots,\""},{"time":287000,"text":"\"Arguing With Idiots.\""},{"time":289000,"text":"They're supposedly tongue-in-cheek,"},{"time":291000,"text":"but they're actually dangerous."},{"time":294000,"text":"Now here's a title that may sound familiar,"},{"time":296000,"text":"but whose author may surprise you:"},{"time":299000,"text":"\"Four-and-a-Half-Years of Struggle"},{"time":301000,"text":"Against Lies, Stupidity"},{"time":303000,"text":"and Cowardice.\""},{"time":305000,"text":"Who wrote that?"},{"time":307000,"text":"That was Adolf Hitler's first title"},{"time":309000,"text":"for \"Mein Kampf\" -- \"My Struggle\" --"},{"time":312000,"text":"the book that launched the Nazi party."},{"time":315000,"text":"The worst eras in human history,"},{"time":317000,"text":"whether in Cambodia or Germany"},{"time":319000,"text":"or Rwanda,"},{"time":321000,"text":"they start like this, with negative other-izing."},{"time":324000,"text":"And then they morph"},{"time":326000,"text":"into violent extremism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329000,"text":"This is why I'm launching a new initiative."},{"time":332000,"text":"And it's to help all of us,"},{"time":335000,"text":"myself included,"},{"time":337000,"text":"to counteract the tendency"},{"time":339000,"text":"to \"otherize.\""},{"time":341000,"text":"And I realize we're all busy people,"},{"time":344000,"text":"so don't worry, you can do this on a lunch break."},{"time":347000,"text":"I'm calling my initiative,"},{"time":349000,"text":"\"Take the Other to Lunch.\""},{"time":352000,"text":"If you are"},{"time":354000,"text":"a Republican,"},{"time":356000,"text":"you can take a Democrat to lunch,"},{"time":359000,"text":"or if you're a Democrat,"},{"time":362000,"text":"think of it"},{"time":364000,"text":"as taking a Republican to lunch."},{"time":366000,"text":"Now if the idea of taking any of these people to lunch"},{"time":369000,"text":"makes you lose your appetite,"},{"time":372000,"text":"I suggest you start more local,"},{"time":375000,"text":"because there is no shortage of the Other"},{"time":378000,"text":"right in your own neighborhood."},{"time":381000,"text":"Maybe that person"},{"time":383000,"text":"who worships at the mosque,"},{"time":385000,"text":"or the church or the synagogue, down the street."},{"time":388000,"text":"Or someone from the other side"},{"time":390000,"text":"of the abortion conflict."},{"time":393000,"text":"Or maybe your brother-in-law"},{"time":395000,"text":"who doesn't believe in global warming."},{"time":398000,"text":"Anyone whose lifestyle may frighten you,"},{"time":403000,"text":"or whose point of view"},{"time":405000,"text":"makes smoke come out of your ears."}]},{"cues":[{"time":409000,"text":"A couple of weeks ago,"},{"time":411000,"text":"I took a Conservative Tea Party woman to lunch."},{"time":416000,"text":"Now on paper, she passed my smoking ears test."},{"time":420000,"text":"She's an activist from the Right,"},{"time":422000,"text":"and I'm an activist from the Left."},{"time":426000,"text":"And we used some guidelines"},{"time":428000,"text":"to keep our conversation elevated,"},{"time":430000,"text":"and you can use them too,"},{"time":432000,"text":"because I know you're all going"},{"time":434000,"text":"to take an Other to lunch."},{"time":436000,"text":"So first of all, decide on a goal:"},{"time":439000,"text":"to get to know one person"},{"time":441000,"text":"from a group you may have negatively stereotyped."},{"time":446000,"text":"And then, before you get together,"},{"time":448000,"text":"agree on some ground rules."},{"time":450000,"text":"My Tea Party lunchmate and I"},{"time":453000,"text":"came up with these:"},{"time":455000,"text":"don't persuade, defend"},{"time":457000,"text":"or interrupt."},{"time":459000,"text":"Be curious;"},{"time":461000,"text":"be conversational; be real."},{"time":463000,"text":"And listen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":465000,"text":"From there, we dove in."},{"time":467000,"text":"And we used these questions:"},{"time":469000,"text":"Share some of your life experiences with me."},{"time":472000,"text":"What issues"},{"time":474000,"text":"deeply concern you?"},{"time":476000,"text":"And what have you always wanted to ask"},{"time":478000,"text":"someone from the other side?"},{"time":481000,"text":"My lunch partner and I"},{"time":483000,"text":"came away with some really important insights,"},{"time":485000,"text":"and I'm going to share just one with you."},{"time":488000,"text":"I think it has relevance"},{"time":490000,"text":"to any problem"},{"time":492000,"text":"between people anywhere."},{"time":494000,"text":"I asked her why her side"},{"time":497000,"text":"makes such outrageous allegations"},{"time":499000,"text":"and lies about my side."},{"time":502000,"text":"\"What?\" she wanted to know."},{"time":504000,"text":"\"Like we're a bunch"},{"time":506000,"text":"of elitist,"},{"time":508000,"text":"morally-corrupt terrorist-lovers.\""},{"time":510000,"text":"Well, she was shocked."},{"time":512000,"text":"She thought my side"},{"time":514000,"text":"beat up on her side way more often,"},{"time":517000,"text":"that we called them brainless,"},{"time":519000,"text":"gun-toting racists,"},{"time":522000,"text":"and we both marveled"},{"time":524000,"text":"at the labels that fit"},{"time":526000,"text":"none of the people"},{"time":528000,"text":"we actually know."},{"time":530000,"text":"And since we had established some trust,"},{"time":532000,"text":"we believed in each other's sincerity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536000,"text":"We agreed we'd speak up in our own communities"},{"time":539000,"text":"when we witnessed"},{"time":541000,"text":"the kind of \"otherizing\" talk"},{"time":543000,"text":"that can wound"},{"time":545000,"text":"and fester into paranoia"},{"time":547000,"text":"and then be used by those on the fringes"},{"time":550000,"text":"to incite."},{"time":552000,"text":"By the end of our lunch,"},{"time":554000,"text":"we acknowledged each other's openness."},{"time":556000,"text":"Neither of us had tried to change the other."},{"time":559000,"text":"But we also hadn't pretended"},{"time":562000,"text":"that our differences were just going to melt away"},{"time":565000,"text":"after a lunch."},{"time":570000,"text":"Instead, we had taken"},{"time":572000,"text":"first steps together,"},{"time":574000,"text":"past our knee-jerk reactions,"},{"time":576000,"text":"to the ubuntu place,"},{"time":578000,"text":"which is the only place"},{"time":580000,"text":"where solutions"},{"time":582000,"text":"to our most intractable-seeming problems"},{"time":586000,"text":"will be found."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588000,"text":"Who should you invite to lunch?"},{"time":591000,"text":"Next time you catch yourself"},{"time":593000,"text":"in the act of otherizing,"},{"time":595000,"text":"that will be your clue."},{"time":597000,"text":"And what might happen at your lunch?"},{"time":600000,"text":"Will the heavens open"},{"time":602000,"text":"and \"We Are the World\" play over the restaurant sound system?"},{"time":605000,"text":"Probably not."},{"time":607000,"text":"Because ubuntu work is slow,"},{"time":609000,"text":"and it's difficult."},{"time":611000,"text":"It's two people"},{"time":613000,"text":"dropping the pretense"},{"time":615000,"text":"of being know-it-alls."},{"time":617000,"text":"It's two people,"},{"time":619000,"text":"two warriors,"},{"time":621000,"text":"dropping their weapons"},{"time":623000,"text":"and reaching toward each other."},{"time":626000,"text":"Here's how the great Persian poet Rumi put it:"},{"time":630000,"text":"\"Out beyond ideas"},{"time":633000,"text":"of wrong-doing and right-doing,"},{"time":636000,"text":"there is a field."},{"time":638000,"text":"I'll meet you there.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":640000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}